oading. It defines defaults and helper methods for protected and hidden class patterns used by Jetty web application environments and server instances.\",\nmetadata/io.quarkus/quarkus-classloader-commons/index.json:9:    \"description\" : \"Quarkus Classloader Commons provides small shared utilities for Quarkus bootstrap class loading. It converts between Java class names and .class resource names and identifies JDK-internal package names used by class loader logic.\",\ntests/src/org.playframework/play-server_3/3.0.0/src/test/scala/org_playframework/play_server_3/ServerSSLEngineTest.scala:158:  private def unused[A]: A = throw new UnsupportedOperationException(\"This test application only exposes class loading\")\ntests/src/org.hibernate.models/hibernate-models/1.0.0/src/test/resources/org_hibernate_models/hibernate_models/simple-class-loading.txt:1:simple class loading resource\ntests/src/org.hibernate.models/hibernate-models/1.0.0/src/test/java/org_hibernate_models/hibernate_models/SimpleClassLoadingTest.java:41:            assertThat(resourceContent).contains(\"simple class loading resource\");\ntests/src/com.diffplug.spotless/spotless-lib-extra/3.0.0/src/test/java/com_diffplug_spotless/spotless_lib_extra/NativeImageDynamicClassLoadingSupport.java:11:final class NativeImageDynamicClassLoadingSupport {\ntests/src/com.diffplug.spotless/spotless-lib-extra/3.0.0/src/test/java/com_diffplug_spotless/spotless_lib_extra/NativeImageDynamicClassLoadingSupport.java:12:    private NativeImageDynamicClassLoadingSupport() {\ntests/src/com.diffplug.spotless/spotless-lib-extra/3.0.0/src/test/java/com_diffplug_spotless/spotless_lib_extra/EclipseJdtFormatterStepTest.java:108:        NativeImageDynamicClassLoadingSupport.rethrowIfNotNativeImageDynamicClassLoadingError(throwable);\ntests/src/com.diffplug.spotless/spotless-lib-extra/3.0.0/src/test/java/com_diffplug_spotless/spotless_lib_extra/EclipseWtpFormatterStepTest.java:104:        NativeImageDynamicClassLoadingSupport.rethrowIf